    <text id="B0691T">
        <front id="d2">
            <div1 type="summary" id="d3">
                <p>Waldo requests that a teacher answer questions pertaining to a school for
                    freedmen.</p>
            </div1>
        </front>

        <body id="d4">
            <div1 type="letter" id="d5">
                <head>
                    Bureau <abbr expan="Refugees, Freedmen and Abandoned Lands">RF and AL</abbr> 4th
                    <abbr expan="Division">Div</abbr> 9 <abbr expan="Sub District">Sub
                        Dist</abbr>
                    <name type="recipient">Miss Mana Bumgarner<lb/>Teacher colored school<lb/>Arbor
                        Hill Augusta <abbr expan="County">Co</abbr>
                        <abbr expan="Virginia">Va</abbr></name>
                </head>

                <opener>
                    <dateline>
                        <date value="1868-10-21"><abbr expan="October">Oct</abbr> 21. 1868</date>
                        <name type="place">Staunton, <abbr expan="Virginia">Va</abbr></name>
                    </dateline>
                    <salute/>
                </opener>

                <p>I enclose herewith Blank School report which please fill out &amp; return to
                    this office by the 28<hi rend="super">th</hi>
                    <abbr expan="instant">inst.</abbr></p>

                <p>It is absolutely necessary that you answer Every question to the best of your
                    ability If any question is asked which does not apply to your duties answer
                    accordingly</p>

                <closer>
                    <salute>Very respectfully</salute>
                    <signed>Roswell Waldo<lb/><abbr expan="Assistant Sub Assistant Commissioner">ASA
                            Comr</abbr></signed>
                    <seg type="postscript">
                        <name type="recipient">Miss Emily Rodney (<abbr expan="colored">c</abbr>)
                            Greenville<lb/>Mr. W. C. <unclear>Echols</unclear> (<abbr
                                expan="colored">c</abbr>) <unclear>West View</unclear></name>
                    </seg>
                </closer>
            </div1>
        </body>
    </text>
